190
00:16:27,078 --> 00:16:29,048
Benar, Ibu. Saya makan malam
bersama perusahaan malam ini.

191
00:16:29,049 --> 00:16:30,717
Jangan tunggu aku.

192
00:16:30,718 --> 00:16:32,624
Jangan lagi.

